Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.84,0:33:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,devoted and they have been for many a\Nlifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.67,0:33:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But they get so far and no more because\Nbeyond that you also need knowledge. You
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.64,0:33:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,also need certain energies and\Nfrequencies in your aura so that when
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.48,0:33:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,you get to that point, it's waiting for\Nyou. Yeah.
