Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.48,0:36:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Because it gives us an orientation\Nto the field. It isn't that we
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.20,0:36:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,necessarily want to know\Nevery particular one, but how does the
