Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.52,0:38:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,po the you know you read Wayne Po that's\Nthe pathway of negation and the pathway
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.76,0:38:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,of Wang Po will take you to 850 850 is\Nthe void
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.07,0:38:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,850 is very very impressive the void is\Nvery very impressive
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.88,0:38:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,there is no\Nuh question about it
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.56,0:38:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,but it is not the ultim it is 850. So\Nthe pathway of negation to to negate the
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.48,0:38:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,reality of all that is linear will take\Nyou to
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.52,0:38:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,unless you've got a teacher that can\Nprepare you in advance to the void to
