Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.11,0:38:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,after writing the book he never wrote\Nanother thing he realized the error he
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.59,0:39:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,himself went to 980 or 90 or something\Nbut he never wrote anything about it so
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.28,0:39:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,we think that Wang Po you know famous in\Nthe Classicist in is the ultimate
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.28,0:39:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,master. He is up to 850. But then at 850\Nyou enter the void which is
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.35,0:39:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,nonlinear, infinite,\Nprofound, silent, unmoving
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.04,0:39:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,with no beginning and no end, universal.\NAnd one thinks this is it. This is what
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.76,0:39:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,has been spoken about over the\Ncenturies.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.40,0:39:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Went back into it. Started this lifetime\Nback at that at age three.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.72,0:39:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Went back to the pathway of negation\Nagain later in life
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.28,0:39:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and ended back in the void again.\NHowever,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.35,0:40:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the difference was\Nat age 12 or 14, something like that, I
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.40,0:40:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,had in a snowbank gotten out of the\Nwind.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.56,0:40:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I got out of the wind. That's all I did\Nis just get out of the wind and suddenly
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.59,0:40:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the presence of infinite love\Nbeyond description
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.92,0:40:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,melted the personal self into the\Neternal beyond time with no beginning no
